"{\"uid\": \"mlsmultiplex.com-posts-usa-faces-an-almost-impossible-mission-against-guinea-at-the-paris-olympics-01j3yhx43g3g\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"This Tuesday at 2pm ET, the destinies of four teams will intertwine at the iconic Stade Geoffroy-Guichard in Saint-\\u00c3\\u0089tienne for the last and decisive round of Group A.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 167, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 159, \"end\": 166, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Group_A\", \"score\": 0.9989419838903063, \"rank\": 0.0010591335398525792, \"text\": \"Group A\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Group_A\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Group_A\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The United States, who entered the Olympic Games with an air of confidence, were harshly brought back to reality when France trounced them with a resounding 3-0 in their opening match.\", \"from\": 169, \"to\": 353, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 287, \"end\": 293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9978623059731154, \"rank\": 0.001925723635549158, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Talk about a wake-up call, right?\", \"from\": 354, \"to\": 387, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the second round, the US demolished New Zealand 4-1, securing not only three precious points but also a goal difference that could prove crucial.\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 536, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 413, \"end\": 415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.999904778334479, \"rank\": 7.250519151174845e-05, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 427, \"end\": 438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\", \"score\": 0.5333823563541509, \"rank\": 0.5149002796600025, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow MLS Multiplex on X (Twitter).\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 574, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And what can we say about the young Kevin Paredes?\", \"from\": 576, \"to\": 626, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 612, \"end\": 625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Paredes\", \"score\": 0.9999854113534683, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kevin Paredes\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Paredes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Paredes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This midfielder, playing for Wolfsburg in the Bundesliga, has been a true maestro on the field.\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 722, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 656, \"end\": 665, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/VfL_Wolfsburg\", \"score\": 0.9999999840442798, \"rank\": 1.5955548175093538e-08, \"text\": \"Wolfsburg\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/VfL_Wolfsburg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/VfL_Wolfsburg\"}, {\"begin\": 673, \"end\": 683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bundesliga\", \"score\": 0.9999962507385843, \"rank\": 3.7133697498114653e-06, \"text\": \"Bundesliga\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bundesliga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bundesliga\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With precise passes and game vision worthy of a veteran, Paredes not only led the victory against New Zealand but also injected hope into a team that seemed destined for failure.\", \"from\": 723, \"to\": 901, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 821, \"end\": 832, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\", \"score\": 0.5333823563541509, \"rank\": 0.5149002796600025, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the other side of the field, we have the Guinea team, facing an almost apocalyptic scenario.\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 998, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Two consecutive defeats\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094a painful opener against New Zealand, losing 2-1, and a more subtle yet equally devastating blow against France, who emerged victorious 1-0.\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1165, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1050, \"end\": 1061, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\", \"score\": 0.5333823563541509, \"rank\": 0.5149002796600025, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1130, \"end\": 1136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9978623059731154, \"rank\": 0.001925723635549158, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Guinea's hopes rest on the shoulders of Amadou Diawara, an experienced midfielder who plays for Belgium's Anderlecht.\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1283, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1206, \"end\": 1220, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amadou_Diawara\", \"score\": 0.9999999176993731, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Amadou Diawara\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amadou_Diawara\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amadou_Diawara\"}, {\"begin\": 1262, \"end\": 1269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999984222132466, \"rank\": 1.5504768964687487e-06, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1272, \"end\": 1282, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/R.S.C._Anderlecht\", \"score\": 0.9999999953270162, \"rank\": 4.672909283960054e-09, \"text\": \"Anderlecht\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/R.S.C._Anderlecht\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/R.S.C._Anderlecht\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But can one man carry the weight of an Olympic dream?\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1337, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It sounds like a mission impossible, but who knows?\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1389, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The other match between New Zealand and France is also of interest to us!\", \"from\": 1391, \"to\": 1464, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1415, \"end\": 1426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\", \"score\": 0.5333823563541509, \"rank\": 0.5149002796600025, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1431, \"end\": 1437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9978623059731154, \"rank\": 0.001925723635549158, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"New Zealand, a team that started with a sparkle in their eyes after defeating Guinea, but had their hopes momentarily dimmed by the loss to the United States, faces the host French team, who need no introduction.\", \"from\": 1465, \"to\": 1677, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1465, \"end\": 1476, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\", \"score\": 0.5333823563541509, \"rank\": 0.5149002796600025, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1639, \"end\": 1645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8238744863259211, \"rank\": 0.20596936288004453, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"France has been a true fortress on the field, and playing at home with fervent support, it's hard to imagine a scenario where they come out defeated.\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1827, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1678, \"end\": 1684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9978623059731154, \"rank\": 0.001925723635549158, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"France has shown why they are considered favorites.\", \"from\": 1828, \"to\": 1879, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1828, \"end\": 1834, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9978623059731154, \"rank\": 0.001925723635549158, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With a dominant performance against the United States and a solid victory over Guinea, the French are cruising smoothly toward the next phase.\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 2022, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1971, \"end\": 1977, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8238744863259211, \"rank\": 0.20596936288004453, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The United States has a chance to continue their path to redemption, while Guinea needs a miracle\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094or two.\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2131, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kevin Paredes and Amadou Diawara will be the names to watch.\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2192, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2132, \"end\": 2145, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Paredes\", \"score\": 0.9999854113534683, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kevin Paredes\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Paredes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Paredes\"}, {\"begin\": 2150, \"end\": 2164, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amadou_Diawara\", \"score\": 0.9999999176993731, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Amadou Diawara\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amadou_Diawara\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amadou_Diawara\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Two players at different stages of their careers, but both carrying the weight of their nations' expe